{"tid":282352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放工時間港鐵又出事　柴灣站故障港島線嚴重受阻","createTime":"2017-06-13T09:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T10:29:46.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b024313ee75b875cb7d8ab9728febf16482b8847","tid":282352,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170613/photo/bkn-20170613174236759-0613_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170613174954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170613%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170613174236759-0613_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170613174954&h=e25e1d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨近打工仔放工繁忙時間，港鐵又發生故障，下午5時27分，運輸署宣布接獲港鐵通知，港島線列車服務受阻，呼籲站內乘客留意車站廣播及職員指示，並預留充裕時間出門。消息稱，由於柴灣站出現訊號故障令服務嚴重受阻，部分列車會於中途站停止服務，以紓緩擠塞情況，乘客可考慮轉乘其他交通工具。"},{"pid":"12060cd498fd2828e3c99a73c4e4c5436bee7791","tid":282352,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32f0ae31385ea861e7f0d9fe88a669674c872dc","tid":282352,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"連玩兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795063f8322a85c7a82446cbb2ddaba487bd2d36","tid":282352,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d8bd8a4b7874f8304b144e31e0782bde7bc716","tid":282352,"uid":1158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"來回都停晒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89596718459334f841